ity-severs-ties-with-all-israeli-universities/0000018f-ce8b-d117-a7ef-ffffeaa00000</guid></item><item><title>明尼苏达大学学术期刊为抵制以色列学者道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</link><description>《文化评论》的编辑写信给一位提交论文供审阅的以色列学者，“我们遗憾地通知您，由于该期刊遵守 BDS 指南，我们无法考虑您提交的论文发表”</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 11:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</link><description>来自凯撒利亚的 24 岁中士（预备）阿达尔·加夫里尔 (Adar Gavriel) 在加沙北部的战斗中阵亡。来自耶路撒冷的 20 岁耶霍纳坦·埃利亚斯中士在加沙南部的战斗中阵亡。以色列国防军表示，在同一事件中，另一名士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府抗议者期待“决定性的”六月，将目光投向耶路撒冷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-anti-government-protesters-look-to-fateful-june-set-sights-on-jerusalem/0000018f-cd76-dc8d-a18f-fdf7fa1f0000</link><description>抗议团体将升级与政府的斗争，并将焦点转向首都，以期在加沙战争一周年之前举行选举并解散议会</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-anti-government-protesters-look-to-fateful-june-set-sights-on-jerusalem/0000018f-cd76-dc8d-a18f-fdf7fa1f0000</guid></item><item><title>影片讲述了 10 月 7 日付出惨重代价的以色列泰国工人群体的心声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.premi