="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/new-labor-leader-yair-golan-wont-be-prime-minister-but-he-might-save-israel-from-itself/0000018f-ca76-d801-a3ef-fb76769a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的高级安全顾问告诉人质家属，他认为政府不会完成人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/netanyahus-top-adviser-to-hostage-families-govt-will-not-complete-hostage-deal/0000018f-cae5-dc8d-a18f-fff558040000</link><description>在第 12 频道新闻报道的一次会议上，国家安全委员会主席查奇·哈内格比 (Tzachi Hanegbi) 告诉人质家庭成员，政府“不会因返回而做出停止战争的决定”，在他们与他对质后，他们侮辱并斥责了他们。所有的人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/netanyahus-top-adviser-to-hostage-families-govt-will-not-complete-hostage-deal/0000018f-cae5-dc8d-a18f-fff558040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长向最高法院提出：政府正在干扰正统派草案命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-high-court-that-the-govt-is-illegally-blocking-haredi-draft-orders/0000018f-cac1-d4da-a58f-ffd9f4d40000</link><description>总检察长巴拉夫-米亚拉写道，政府试图阻止她的办公室“确保犹太学院学生起草命令的适当程序”符合最高法院的裁决，“是非法的”。由九名法官组成的扩大小组将于周日审理反对征兵豁免的请愿书</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-high-court-that-the-govt-is-illegally-blocking-haredi-draft-orders/0000018f-cac1-d4da-a58f-ffd9f4d40000</guid></item><item><title>“没有秘密警察”：以色列辛贝特拒绝加强对反内塔尼亚胡抗议者的监视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-declined-to-step-up-surveillance-of-anti-netanyahu-protesters/0000018f-cab3-d4da-a58f-fffbb3e60000</link><description>辛贝特安全部门负责人最近被要求加强对民主抗议活动的监视。 “我们不会成为秘密警察，”他回答道</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-declined-to-step-up-surveillance-of-anti-